item.title: CVE-2020-5596|2024-08-04T08:30:24.615Z -- mitsubishi%20electric%20corporation -- got2000%20series%20gt27%2C%20gt25%2C%20and%20gt23
item.description: TCP/IP function included in the firmware of Mitsubishi Electric GOT2000 series (CoreOS with version -Y and earlier installed in GT27 Model, GT25 Model, and GT23 Model) does not properly manage sessions, which may allow a remote attacker to stop the network functions of the products or execute a malicious program via a specially crafted packet.
